description: This charming and character-filled East Side condo checks all the boxes! Featuring beautiful hardwood floors, exposed brick, crown molding, and a cozy gas fireplace, this home seamlessly blends classic detail with modern convenience. The chef’s kitchen is equipped with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances, opening to a warm and inviting living room—ideal for entertaining. The oversized king bedroom features French doors that lead to a bonus office or den, perfect for working from home or relaxing. Enjoy rare outdoor space with a spacious private yard, plus central A/C, in-unit laundry, and unbeatable proximity—just one block to East Broadway’s restaurants, shops, and everyday essentials. Take a short stroll to Castle Island and the beach for the ultimate Southie lifestyle. An incredible opportunity for a first-time homebuyer or city dweller seeking comfort, charm, and location.
